'''詹姆斯·皮爾森'''（{{lang-en|'''James Pearson'''}}；{{bd|1993年|1月19日}}）是一位已退役[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是中後衛或右邊衛<ref name="nas">{{cite web|title=Carlisle Utd Facing Four Cup Finals, Says Loan Man Pearson|url=http://www.newsandstar.co.uk/carlisle-united/latest/carlisle-utd-facing-four-cup-finals-says-loan-man-pearson-1.1122986|publisher=The Cumberland News & Star|date=14 March 2014|accessdate=20 March 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317074930/http://www.newsandstar.co.uk/carlisle-united/latest/carlisle-utd-facing-four-cup-finals-says-loan-man-pearson-1.1122986|archivedate=2014年3月17日}}</ref>。他是英格蘭足球運動員及教練[[尼格尔·皮尔逊|尼格尔·皮尔逊]]之子。

==職業生涯==
皮爾森在[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|罗瑟勒姆]]展開其足球生涯，但在2009年夏天被球會放棄<ref name="nas">{{cite web|title=Carlisle Utd Facing Four Cup Finals, Says Loan Man Pearson|url=http://www.newsandstar.co.uk/carlisle-united/latest/carlisle-utd-facing-four-cup-finals-says-loan-man-pearson-1.1122986|publisher=The Cumberland News & Star|date=14 March 2014|accessdate=20 March 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317074930/http://www.newsandstar.co.uk/carlisle-united/latest/carlisle-utd-facing-four-cup-finals-says-loan-man-pearson-1.1122986|archivedate=2014年3月17日}}</ref>。經歷一年無球會落腳的賽季後，在2012年9月19日，他加盟父親所執教的英冠球會[[萊斯特城足球俱樂部|萊斯特城]]，簽約一年<ref>{{cite web|title=Nigel Pearson signs son James for Leicester City|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19650945|publisher=BBC Sport|date=19 September 2012|accessdate=20 March 2014|archive-date=2016-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117163206/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19650945|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年3月11日，皮爾森被外借到[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[卡莱尔联足球俱乐部|卡莱尔联]]至季末<ref name="loan">{{cite web|title=Carlisle sign Leicester's James Pearson & Watford's Reece Brown|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/26533668|publisher=BBC|4=|date=11 March 2014|accessdate=19 March 2014|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924202716/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/26533668|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外借翌日便首次在職業聯賽上場，該場以1-0不敵[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|谢菲尔德联]]的比賽踢滿90分鐘<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheff Utd 1-0 Carlisle|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/26444940|accessdate=31 May 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=12 March 2014|archive-date=2014-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314113131/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/26444940|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年6月2日，他獲得萊斯特城續約一年<ref>{{cite web|title=Deals for Development Squad Duo|url=http://www.lcfc.com/news/article/020514-deals-for-development-squad-duo-1593010.aspx|publisher=Leicester City FC|date=2 June 2014|access-date=2015-07-14|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714210749/http://www.lcfc.com/news/article/020514-deals-for-development-squad-duo-1593010.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年8月26日，皮爾森首次代表萊斯特城上場參加[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第二輪對[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|谢斯伯利]]的比賽並踢滿全場<ref>{{cite news|title=Leicester 0-1 Shrewsbury|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28846954|accessdate=31 May 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=26 August 2014|archive-date=2015-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151102153110/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28846954|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月27日，他被外借到[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|全國聯]]球會[[雷克斯汉姆足球俱乐部|雷克斯汉姆]]一個月<ref>{{cite news|title=Leicester City defender James Pearson joins Wrexham on loan|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29798776|accessdate=31 May 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=28 October 2014|archive-date=2015-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223172851/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29798776|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後來延長至2015年1月<ref>{{cite news|title=Wrexham extend Leicester defender James Pearson's loan|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30252860|accessdate=31 May 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=28 November 2014|archive-date=2014-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141202132949/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30252860|dead-url=no}}</ref>，期間代表球會在聯賽上場5次、[[英格蘭足總錦標|英格蘭足總錦標]]2次及[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]第三輪以3-1不敵[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|斯托克城]]的賽事<ref>{{cite news|last1=Reddy|first1=Luke|title=Stoke 3-1 Wrexham|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30614401|accessdate=31 May 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=4 January 2015|archive-date=2015-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707235405/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30614401|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年3月，他被外借至[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼得伯勒联]]至季末，但期間沒有任何上場紀錄<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lcfc.com/news/article/peterborough-loan-for-pearson-2359654.aspx |title=Peterborough Loan For James Pearson |access-date=2021-05-11 |archive-date=2016-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625144702/http://www.lcfc.com/news/article/peterborough-loan-for-pearson-2359654.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年5月季後他隨球隊前往泰國參加推廣活動。然而他與隊友[[湯姆·霍柏|湯姆·霍柏]]和[[亞當·史密斯_(1992年出生足球運動員)|亞當·史密斯]]在泰國期間嫖妓及種族歧視一事被曝光，片段被公開。三人雖然隨即為事件及受影響的女子道歉<ref>{{cite news|title=Leicester City trio apologise for behaviour on Thailandtour|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-leicestershire-32950519|accessdate=31 May 2015|work=BBC News|date=31 May 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108090927/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-leicestershire-32950519|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最終三人在6月17日被球會解約<ref>{{cite news|title=Leicester City: Three players sacked following racist sex tape|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33175820|accessdate=17 June 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=17 June 2015|archive-date=2015-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703140549/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33175820|dead-url=no}}</ref>。詹姆斯父親亦因此事在6月30日被球會革退<ref>{{cite news|title=Nigel Pearson: Leicester boss's sacking linked to son's actions|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33339566|accessdate=1 July 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=1 July 2015|archive-date=2016-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117163206/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33339566|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

離開李斯特城後，成為自由身的皮爾森回到[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|罗瑟勒姆]]繼續訓練<ref>[http://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/James-Pearson-training-Rotherham-United-months/story-27809378-detail/story.html "James Pearson training with Rotherham United months after sacking over 'racist orgy' in Thailand"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/James-Pearson-training-Rotherham-United-months/story-27809378-detail/story.html |date=20150918043004 }} by David W. Owen, ''Leicester Mercury''</ref>，並在2016年2月2日與[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|巴尼特]]以非合約方式加盟<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35476521 "James Pearson: Barnet sign former Leicester defender"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35476521 |date=20210513132719 }}, ''BBC Sport'', 2 February 2016</ref><ref>[http://www.barnetfc.com/news/article/james-pearson-signs-for-barnet-2934976.aspx "James Pearson signs for Barnet!"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.barnetfc.com/news/article/james-pearson-signs-for-barnet-2934976.aspx |date=20170510172731 }}, Barnet F.C. website, 2 February 2016</ref>。3月雙方正式簽訂合約至2017年夏天<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35727627 |title=James Pearson: Former Leicester City defender signs new Barnet contract |access-date=2021-05-11 |archive-date=2021-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513035522/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35727627 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016/17球季季前集訓期間他受了傷，使他缺席整個球季，並在季後約滿離隊<ref>[http://www.barnet-today.co.uk/article.cfm?id=118742&headline=Trio%20to%20leave%20Barnet%20after%20not%20being%20offered%20new%20contracts&sectionIs=sport&searchyear=2017 Trio to leave Barnet after not being offered new contracts]</ref>。

2017年8月4日他以非合約方式轉投[[考文垂足球俱乐部|考文垂]]，但不到一個月便被釋出，沒有代表球隊上場<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ccfc.co.uk/news/2017/august/news-james-pearson-leaves-the-sky-blues/ |title=NEWS: James Pearson leaves the Sky Blues |access-date=2021-05-11 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511211936/https://www.ccfc.co.uk/news/2017/august/news-james-pearson-leaves-the-sky-blues/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之後他加盟先後[[京达米士特足球俱乐部|京达米士特]]和[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|马科斯菲尔德]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Pearson Added To Kidderminster Squad|url=http://nonleague.pitchero.com/headlines/pearson-added-kidderminster-squad/|accessdate=16 September 2017|work=Non League Pitchero|date=15 September 2017|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512224143/https://nonleague.pitchero.com/headlines/pearson-added-kidderminster-squad/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年10月，他接受[[衛報|衛報]]訪問時因為傷患問題，使他退出足球員生涯<ref>{{cite news |last1=Fisher |first1=Ben |title='Players were in tears': what it was really like as Macclesfield collapsed |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/oct/07/players-were-in-tears-macclesfield-collapse-league-two-james-pearson |accessdate=7 October 2020 |work=The Guardian |date=7 October 2020 |archive-date=2021-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512071947/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/oct/07/players-were-in-tears-macclesfield-collapse-league-two-james-pearson |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

